    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Said to be fiendish relations of all goblinoid races, the hateful barghests come to the Material Plane to feed. As they consume the bodies of innocents, they grow increasingly powerful. A barghest eventually sheds its skin to transform into a greater barghest, at which point it often seeks out a tribe of goblins or other creatures to rule."
        }
    ],
